Capitec Bank Adds 890,000 New Clients Since February, Stassen Says

-- B y   S i k o n a t h i   M a n t s h a n t s h a
-- 
2011-06-06T06:28:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/capitec-bank-adds-890-000-new-clients-since-february-stassen-says.html
  Capitec Bank Holdings Ltd. (CPI) ,  South
Africa ’s fastest-growing bank, has gained 890,000 new clients
since February, taking the total number to 3 million, according
to the bank’s Chief Executive Officer Riaan Stassen told
shareholders at an annual meeting of shareholders on June 3,
Business Day newspaper reported.  “While attracting new clients is fundamental to the bank’s
growth, keeping them is too,” he added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sikonathi Mantshantsha in Johannesburg at 
 smantshantsh@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
